extendedInfo.description: Find the key of any song or melody by playing it into your phone! Based on modern pitch and key detection algorithms, Song Key Finder provides astonishing results. Great for bands, DJs using harmonic mixing, songwriters, tabulature transcribers, and anyone interested in learning how to play their favorite songs.Supports all phone and tablet resolutions with sharp HD graphics. If you want to use an external mic, just select it from the "Mic" options in the Main Menu.This app contains ZERO push, notification, icon, or ringback advertising.

reviews.title: Not functioning (period)
reviews.comment: The app simply does not work. It force closes every time you select \'listen\' to analyze a track. As a developer, my guess would be the file size and possibly too many tasks occurring at once (within the app) are causing the force close. Very disappointing, and it goes without saying that this is a waste of time. I\'m not sure if the pro version would be any better or not, but if they cannot even make a functioning app I doubt the other versions would be any different. Tested on an LG E-739.
reviews.author: Adam Shapiro
